**Coroner** | Townsfolk Miscellaneous
__Basics__
Upon every death, the Coroner is informed how that participant died. 
__Details__
The Coroner will be told the cause of death for every dead player, and if multiple causes of death are present, then all causes will be revealed to the Coroner. 
The Coroner is told the name of role that killed the player (if applicable) and the type of death (this can be either “kill”, “suicide”, “lynch” or “descension”), as well as the name (but not the role) of the player that died. 
The Coroner is not affected by any disguises.

__Simplified__
Upon every death, the Coroner is informed how that participant died.

__Formalized__
On @All Death: Learn `@This died by @DeathType from @Attacker`

__Card__
The Coroner will learn how a player died.
